snippet.title: The Dark Pictures Anthology: House of Ashes - Story Trailer & Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Deep underground, something evil has awakened. 

Descend into the underworld in The Dark Pictures Anthology: House of Ashes, coming to PS4/PS5, Xbox One & Series X|S and PC on 22 October 2021. 
Pre-order: https://bnent.eu/HOA_Preorder
